# Logging Configuration

## System

**Dual-handler logging**: Clean terminal (INFO+) + complete file audit (DEBUG+)

### Log Files
- `elysia/logs/elysia.log` - All Python app logs (DEBUG)
- `elysia/logs/uvicorn.log` - HTTP server traffic (INFO)
- `elysia/logs/sessions.jsonl` - Session records
- `elysia/logs/sessions/` - Per-session detailed logs

---

## Usage

```python
from elysia.api.core.log import logger

logger.debug("Diagnostic details")  # File only
logger.info("Important milestone")  # File + console
logger.warning("Unexpected condition")  # File + console
logger.error("Operation failed")  # File + console
```

---

## Monitor

```bash
# All events
tail -f elysia/logs/elysia.log

# HTTP traffic
tail -f elysia/logs/uvicorn.log

# Search errors
grep ERROR elysia/logs/elysia.log
```

---

## Control Verbosity

```bash
elysia start --log-level debug    # Debug to console
elysia start --log-level warning  # Minimal console
```

Default: INFO to console, DEBUG to file.

